                    <li>A PHP version upper or equal to 5.5.9 </li>
                    <li>Composer must be installed
                        <br/><br/>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li><kbd style="margin-top: 20px">curl -sS https://getcomposer.org/installer | php</kbd></li>
                            <li><kbd> sudo mv composer.phar /usr/local/bin/composer.phar</kbd></li>
